window.SLIDES = {"00": ["<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/WBM-EHQGsxyNXlQFbcPfi.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><labels><label variant=\"solid\">Module 00</label></labels><display size=\"md\">What You'll Build</display><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/joF2VqDZc_qb7_TVZhLbF.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Your Week, Right Now</h1><smart-layout cell-size=\"15\" variant=\"solidJoinedBoxes\"><smart-layout-item id=\"UHpTn\"><h4>Open a Role</h4><p>Hunt for candidates one tab at a time. Read profile after profile.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"G5wpK\"><h4>Write Outreach</h4><p>Until every message sounds the same. Real work, but mechanical.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"JEv0L\"><h4>Hand It Off</h4><p>Mechanical work is what we hand to AI agents. That is the shift.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img alt=\"illustrated cartoon robot with friendly face sitting at a microphone, podcast studio setting, flat vector style\" id=\"VEaJb\" meta='{\"width\":1920,\"height\":1088}' source=\"image.ai-generated\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/dljDSjikSdLZzkUJlDme9.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><labels><label variant=\"outline\">Your Host</label></labels><h1>Meet Ada</h1><p>An AI voice. Yes, really. This whole course is narrated by an agent, because the best way to show what these tools do is to use them.</p><aside variant=\"info\"><p>No code. No technical background required. If you can use Gmail and LinkedIn, you can build this.</p></aside></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>What Is an AI Agent?</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img class=\"g-info\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/VKSdL2EtNNWTPPb_.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><p>Software that uses an AI model to do a task that normally needs a person to think a little.</p><smart-layout cell-size=\"10\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item id=\"W_FIA\"><h4>It Reads</h4><p>Takes in text, profiles, job descriptions, and context.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"H4lCD\"><h4>It Judges</h4><p>Applies reasoning, not just rigid keyword rules.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"66Fnh\"><h4>It Produces</h4><p>Something useful: a ranked list, a score, a draft message.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>You Will Build Three Agents</h1><smart-layout cell-size=\"15\" variant=\"solidBoxesWithIconsInside\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/magnifying-glass.svg\"/><div><h4>Sourcing Agent</h4><p>Finds and lists candidates. Free sources only. No paid tools required.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/bars.svg\"/><div><h4>Screening Agent</h4><p>Scores fit before you read a single profile. Saves hours of first-pass review.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/envelope.svg\"/><div><h4>Outreach Agent</h4><p>Drafts a personalized first message in your voice. Every time.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/BWkh9O8Q04rvqv-sBCzO-.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The End-State: Your Recruiting Operating System</h1><aside variant=\"success\"><p>The machine sorts and drafts. A human always sends. That is a rule, not an accident.</p></aside><p>Job Opened, then the Sourcing Agent, then the Screening Agent, then the Outreach Agent, then a Human Reviews and sends.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Why Recruiters Win with AI Now</h1><smart-layout cell-size=\"15\" numbered=\"false\" variant=\"bigBullets\"><smart-layout-item id=\"o8w1V\"><h4>Text In, Text Out</h4><p>Your work is almost entirely words. That makes it ideal for AI.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"FvIdI\"><h4>The Boring 70% Is Automatable</h4><p>Sourcing, first-pass screening, first-draft outreach. All of it.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"DFLsm\"><h4>Your Edge Moves Up</h4><p>Judgment and relationships. The part no tool can copy.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/DYnmnaAc-Z6QNYw5eFe1v.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><display size=\"lg\">Do</display><p>A recruiter who does the work juggles a few roles at a time.</p></div><div class=\"g-colorpanel\" style=\"background:#6C3FC5;color:#fff;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:10px;flex:50 1 0\"><display size=\"lg\">Run</display><p>A recruiter who runs a system handles many more.</p></div></columns><h1>The Mindset Shift</h1><p>From doing the work, to running the system that does the work. That is the entire course in one sentence.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Your First Asset: The Time Audit</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><p>For two working days, log every task switch in one line. Then sort into four buckets.</p><smart-layout cell-size=\"10\" numbered=\"true\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithLabel\"><smart-layout-item id=\"VbC4V\"><h4>Sourcing</h4></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"DLkZb\"><h4>Screening</h4></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"z8MHv\"><h4>Outreach</h4></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item id=\"kGcDv\"><h4>Human-Only</h4></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><aside><p>Total the first three buckets. That is the time this course gives back to you.</p></aside><p>The audit is not homework. It is your baseline. You cannot measure what you have not tracked.</p></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h4>Coming Up</h4><h1>Next: Module 01</h1><display size=\"md\">AI Foundations for Recruiters</display><smart-layout cell-size=\"15\" numbered=\"false\" variant=\"pills\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/star.svg\"/><div><h4>What AI Is Great At</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/engine-warning.svg\"/><div><h4>Where It Lies to You</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/i-cursor.svg\"/><div><h4>Your First Real Prompt</h4></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/whFg7_B4ZZZ1CPmYe6Czb.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>"], "01": ["<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/4XNBFK0A3AyMAMuIufmDo.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><h4>Module 01: AI Foundations for Recruiters</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>One Mental Model: A Very Advanced Autocomplete</h1><p>The AI behind every agent you will build predicts what words come next, given what you wrote. That simple idea covers a huge slice of recruiting.</p><smart-layout cell-size=\"15\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>You write something</h4><p>A job spec, a candidate profile, a search query.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>AI predicts what comes next</h4><p>The most sensible continuation of your text.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>You get useful output</h4><p>A summary, a draft, a score, a boolean string.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/5vqalYsk8ouRQM-gVXTal.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Predicting the Next Words Covers Your Job</h1><p>Every core recruiting task is a text-in, text-out operation. The model does not need to understand recruiting. It just needs to predict well.</p><smart-layout cell-size=\"20\" image-position=\"top\" variant=\"iconsText\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/passport.svg\"/><div><h4>Summarize a Profile</h4><p>Given a raw LinkedIn export, produce a clean one-paragraph summary.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/envelopes.svg\"/><div><h4>Draft a Message</h4><p>Given a job and a candidate, write a personalized outreach note.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/searchengin.svg\"/><div><h4>Build a Search String</h4><p>Turn a job spec into a boolean string ready for LinkedIn or GitHub.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/bars.svg\"/><div><h4>Compare to Requirements</h4><p>Score a candidate profile against your criteria, field by field.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Where AI Is Reliable Today</h1><aside variant=\"success\"><p>Text in, text out. These are the high-trust tasks.</p></aside><smart-layout cell-size=\"15\" variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Summarizing</h4><p>Condense a long profile into a short, structured brief.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Rewriting and Drafting</h4><p>Polish a job description or write an outreach message from scratch.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Extracting Fields</h4><p>Pull structured data from messy, unformatted text.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Comparing and Scoring</h4><p>Match a profile to criteria and return a structured score.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Transforming</h4><p>Convert a job description into a boolean search string.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/usSiBshQKApEOmmk-FYkg.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Where It Lies to You</h1><aside variant=\"caution\"><p>Never trust AI for facts you did not give it.</p></aside><smart-layout cell-size=\"20\" numbered=\"true\" variant=\"bigBullets\"><smart-layout-item><h4>It makes things up, confidently.</h4><p>This is hallucination. The model produces plausible-sounding text that is simply wrong.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>It does not know today.</h4><p>It has a knowledge cutoff. Recent events, new companies, and current roles are invisible to it.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>It is confident even when wrong.</h4><p>There is no built-in uncertainty signal. Wrong answers look identical to correct ones.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>It carries bias from its training text.</h4><p>The data it learned from reflects historical patterns, including unfair ones.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Two Habits That Keep You Safe</h1><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" source=\"image.ai-generated\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/OszwblEqh6mUkvhi-OHXs.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><smart-layout cell-size=\"10\" numbered=\"true\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithLabel\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Give It the Source</h4><p>Paste the profile directly into the prompt. Never ask the model to recall a real person from memory. The model only knows what you give it in that moment.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Keep a Human on Facts and on Send</h4><p>The model drafts and scores. You verify and send. No AI output goes to a candidate or client without a human check. This is non-negotiable.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Task Map</h1><p>Not every recruiting task belongs to an AI agent. Here is how to split them.</p><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img class=\"g-info\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/MJRRRGGRH0tz5KnI.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><aside variant=\"success\"><p>High trust: you gave the source. Summarize, score, draft. Your agents live here.</p></aside><aside variant=\"warning\"><p>Low trust: stays with you. Finding facts, making final decisions, sending anything.</p></aside><p>The rule is simple. If you supplied the text, the model can work with it. If the model has to go find something on its own, keep a human in the loop.</p></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/66nQjFrT73-IK2NQqTwvY.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Your First Prompt: Role, Context, Task, Format</h1><p>Give the model four things, plus one truth line.</p><smart-layout cell-size=\"20\" orientation=\"vertical\" variant=\"arrows\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Role</h4><p>Tell the model who it is. \"You are an expert tech recruiter.\"</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Context</h4><p>Paste the profile or job spec. Give it the source material.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Task</h4><p>State exactly what you want. Summarize, score, draft, extract.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Format</h4><p>Specify the output shape. Bullet list, table, one paragraph.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside><p>Truth line: Do not invent any facts. Only use the profile. Say \"not stated\" when something is missing.</p></aside></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Prompt in Action</h1><p>A dummy profile for Alex R. drops into the prompt. Here is what comes out.</p><columns col-widths=\"[45,55]\"><div style=\"flex:45 1 0\"><h4>Input: Alex R. Profile</h4><pre><code>Name: Alex R.\nTitle: Senior Backend Engineer\nYears of experience: 7\nSkills: Python, Go, Kubernetes\nEducation: Not stated\nLocation: Remote</code></pre></div><div style=\"flex:55 1 0\"><h4>Output: AI Summary</h4><smart-layout cell-size=\"10\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>One-Line Summary</h4><p>Senior backend engineer with 7 years in Python and Go, experienced in Kubernetes-based infrastructure.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Three Strengths</h4><p>Backend depth. Cloud-native tooling. Multi-language fluency.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Seniority Estimate</h4><p>Senior. Consistent with 7 years and scope of skills listed.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Open Question</h4><p>Education: not stated. Team leadership experience: not stated.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Your Asset: The Candidate Profile Summarizer</h1><blockquote><p>Save the prompt. In Module 06 you turn this exact prompt into an automated agent.</p></blockquote><smart-layout cell-size=\"15\" numbered=\"true\" variant=\"processSteps\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Run the prompt by hand</h4><p>Paste a real profile for Alex R. or any candidate. Confirm the output looks right. Adjust the format line if needed.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Save it somewhere you can find it</h4><p>A text file, a Notion page, a Google Doc. Label it clearly: Candidate Profile Summarizer v1.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Automate it in Module 06</h4><p>This exact prompt becomes the core of your first automated agent. Run it by hand first, then automate it.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/5k01cZWTUTW3iFdETOo_r.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/IFwu-gXm8VSAwXB7ac9RT.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Next: Module 02</h1><h4>Prompting for Sourcing and Screening</h4><p>From one good prompt to a whole library, tuned to your niche. Keep your summarizer handy.</p><smart-layout cell-size=\"20\" variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>What You Built in Module 01</h4><p>A mental model for AI. A clear map of trust. Your first structured prompt. The Candidate Profile Summarizer.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>What Is Coming in Module 02</h4><p>Sourcing prompts. Screening prompts. A full prompt library tuned to your niche and your candidates.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"info\"><p>Ada will see you in Module 02. Bring your summarizer.</p></aside></div></div>"], "02": ["<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/y6gEpDzWV0-qQdAqQilrr.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><h4>Module 02: Prompting for Sourcing and Screening</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>A Secret About Everything You Will Build</h1><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>The Sourcing Agent</h4><p>Just a good prompt running on autopilot.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>The Screening Agent</h4><p>Just a good prompt running on autopilot.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>The Outreach Agent</h4><p>Just a good prompt running on autopilot.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"warning\"><p>A weak prompt automated only gives you weak results faster. This module is the real leverage.</p></aside></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/OIC8T5r69XmxcOtPvGTWt.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Anatomy of a Strong Prompt: R-C-T-F</h1><smart-layout orientation=\"landscape\" variant=\"arrows\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/person.svg\"/><div><h4>Role</h4><p>Who the model acts as. \"You are an expert technical sourcer.\"</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/passport.svg\"/><div><h4>Context</h4><p>The facts it may use. The job spec, the profile, your constraints.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/reflect-both.svg\"/><div><h4>Task</h4><p>The one job to do. \"Write a boolean search string.\"</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/table-layout.svg\"/><div><h4>Format</h4><p>The exact shape of the answer. \"Return only the string.\"</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Two Habits That Separate Good from Great</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>Constrain the Truth</h4><p>Add one line to every prompt that touches a real person:</p><blockquote><p>\"Do not invent any facts, use only what I gave you.\"</p></blockquote><p>This is what protects you from hallucination. Keep it in every prompt.</p></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>Show One Example</h4><p>Paste one good answer and the model copies the pattern fast.</p><aside variant=\"success\"><p>A single example is worth a paragraph of instructions. Show, do not just tell.</p></aside></div></columns></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/rQ-9fOe8kqSujs0g2mMf9.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Weak Prompt</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><pre><code>\"write an outreach message to a backend developer\"</code></pre><labels><label variant=\"solid\">The Prompt</label></labels><p>No role. No context. No constraints. No format.</p></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><aside variant=\"caution\"><p>Result: a generic, templated message that screams copy and paste. The candidate sees it immediately and ignores it.</p></aside><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>No Role Defined</h4></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>No Context Given</h4></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>No Format Set</h4></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Strong Prompt</h1><columns col-widths=\"[55,45]\"><div style=\"flex:55 1 0\"><labels><label variant=\"solid\">The Prompt</label></labels><pre><code>Role: A warm, concise recruiter.\nContext: Senior backend role, fintech\nscale-up, remote. Candidate Alex R.,\nPython and Go.\nTone: Direct, friendly, under 90 words.\nFormat: No \"I hope this finds you well.\"\nOpen with one specific reason.\nEnd with a low-pressure question.\nDo not invent facts.</code></pre></div><div style=\"flex:45 1 0\"><aside variant=\"success\"><p>Result: a message that sounds like you wrote it for that one person, Alex R. Specific. Human. Effective.</p></aside><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Role Defined</h4><p>Warm, concise recruiter</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Context Loaded</h4><p>Fintech, remote, Alex R.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Format Locked</h4><p>Under 90 words, no filler</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/VoJVe8CC4rATm__7LP_iX.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Your 10-Prompt Library</h1><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Sourcing</h4><ul><li>Boolean Builder</li><li>X-ray Builder</li><li>Keyword Expander</li><li>Role Intake</li></ul></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Screening</h4><ul><li>Profile Summarizer</li><li>Fit Scorer</li><li>Red-flag Scanner</li><li>Candidate Comparator</li></ul></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Communication</h4><ul><li>Outreach Drafter</li><li>Respectful Decline</li></ul></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Make the Library Yours</h1><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" variant=\"processSteps\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Change Every Role Line to Your Niche</h4><p>Replace the generic role with your specialty. \"Fintech backend recruiter.\" \"Cyber security headhunter.\" The more specific, the better the output.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Teach the Outreach Drafter Your Voice</h4><p>Paste two real messages you are proud of. The model learns your tone, your rhythm, your style. Alex R. gets a message that sounds like you.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Save Your Versions Where You Work Every Day</h4><p>Keep your customized prompts in your daily workflow tool. A prompt you cannot find is a prompt you will not use.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Do This Now: Run the Pipeline by Hand</h1><p>Pick one open role. Run these three prompts in sequence:</p><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" variant=\"pills\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/searchengin.svg\"/><div><h4>Boolean Builder</h4><p>Generate a search string for your open role.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/person.svg\"/><div><h4>Profile Summarizer</h4><p>Summarize a candidate like Alex R. from their profile.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/envelope.svg\"/><div><h4>Outreach Drafter</h4><p>Write a tailored message for that candidate.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"success\"><p>You just ran the whole pipeline. In the build modules, each step becomes an agent.</p></aside></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/8_BLIxeLsutcGpG4oQEjQ.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/o81B2B0vdc4hOFCin6NkM.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Next: Module 03</h1><h4>Workflow vs Agent: Choosing the Right Build</h4><p>Not every task needs a reasoning agent. Knowing the difference saves you weeks.</p><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>What You Will Learn</h4><p>When to use a simple workflow and when to build a true agent. The wrong choice costs time and money.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>What to Bring</h4><p>Your customized 10-prompt library, tailored to your niche and your voice. You will need it.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>"], "03": ["<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/kxMmLLpZ3Uh13P-gruV6g.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><h4>Module 03: Workflow vs Agent, Choosing the Right Build</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/VfVJam6vbTDrCHll-8mrg.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Trap: Do Not Make Everything an Agent</h1><aside variant=\"warning\"><p>The most common beginner mistake is building a complex reasoning agent for a task that only needed five fixed steps.</p></aside><p>It costs more, breaks more, and is harder to fix. One decision keeps you out of that trap.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Two Words, Defined Simply</h1><smart-layout variant=\"solidJoinedBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Workflow</h4><p>A fixed set of steps that runs the same way every time. No judgment. A recipe.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Agent</h4><p>Software that uses AI to make a judgment when the input varies. It thinks, within limits.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/5V9yYPr3crCgONz8TeKQT.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Real Answer: A Workflow with a Brain</h1><p>Almost every automation is a workflow with one or two AI steps inside.</p><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>The Workflow Handles</h4><ul><li>Triggers</li><li>Moving data</li><li>Writing to sheets</li></ul></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>The AI Step Handles</h4><ul><li>The one moment that needs judgment</li><li>Variable input</li><li>Reasoning within limits</li></ul></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Example: Your Screening Agent</h1><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/bolt.svg\"/><span>Trigger</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://gamma.app/api/icons/file.svg?provider=fa&amp;style=light\"/><span>Get Profile</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/brain.svg\"/><span>AI Judges Fit</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/pencil.svg\"/><span>Write Score</span></div></div><p>Only the middle step needs a brain. Everything around it is plain workflow. The AI judgment is the one moment of intelligence in an otherwise fixed sequence.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Decision Framework: Three Questions</h1><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithTopCircle\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Can I write the exact steps, and they never change?</h4><p>Yes means workflow.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Does it need judgment, or does the input vary?</h4><p>Yes means add an AI step.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Must the AI choose between many tools on its own?</h4><p>Rarely. Only then a full agent.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Cost of Complexity</h1><smart-layout variant=\"staircase\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Workflow</h4><p>Fast, tiny cost, predictable, easy to debug.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Workflow with AI Step</h4><p>Still cheap and clear. The professional sweet spot.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Full Autonomous Agent</h4><p>Slow, pricier, least predictable, hardest to fix.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"success\"><p>Default to simple. It is the professional choice.</p></aside></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/G9MDVFGL_Gfk4ux-pllzr.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Map Your Own Tasks</h1><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Pure Workflow</h4><ul><li>Follow-up reminders</li><li>Stage moves</li><li>Logging</li><li>Formatting a shortlist</li></ul></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Workflow with AI Step</h4><ul><li>Screening</li><li>Drafting outreach</li><li>Summarizing a CV</li></ul></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Human Only</h4><ul><li>Final hiring decisions</li><li>Sensitive conversations</li></ul></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Your Three Builds All Land in the Middle</h1><smart-layout image-position=\"top\" variant=\"iconsText\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/searchengin.svg\"/><div><h4>Sourcing</h4><p>A workflow with a single AI step doing the thinking.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/bars.svg\"/><div><h4>Screening</h4><p>A workflow with a single AI step doing the thinking.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/messages.svg\"/><div><h4>Outreach</h4><p>A workflow with a single AI step doing the thinking.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside><p>That is the pattern, not a coincidence.</p></aside></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Your Asset: The Decision Sheet</h1><p>Take three real tasks. For each, fill in the four columns below. That is your honest build plan.</p><table col-widths=\"[25,25,25,25]\"><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Trigger</b></p></td><td><p><b>Fixed Steps</b></p></td><td><p><b>Judgment Needed?</b></p></td><td><p><b>Verdict</b></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Task 1 trigger</p></td><td><p>List the steps</p></td><td><p>Yes or No</p></td><td><p>Workflow / AI Step / Agent</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Task 2 trigger</p></td><td><p>List the steps</p></td><td><p>Yes or No</p></td><td><p>Workflow / AI Step / Agent</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Task 3 trigger</p></td><td><p>List the steps</p></td><td><p>Yes or No</p></td><td><p>Workflow / AI Step / Agent</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/HEVz-xMtpRp_KBQYrlnF5.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Next: Module 04</h1><h4>Your Toolkit and First Automation</h4><p>You finally open n8n and build a plain workflow with one AI step. Bring your Decision Sheet.</p><aside variant=\"info\"><p>Complete your Decision Sheet before the next module. Three tasks, four columns, one honest verdict each.</p></aside></div></div>"], "04": ["<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><labels><label variant=\"solid\">Module 04</label></labels><h4>Your Toolkit and First Automation</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/XFZVnnkT9TV2RvO4V4_D-.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Today you build something that runs without you</h1><p>A plain workflow with one AI step, made real. By the end you have a working automation: text in, AI summary out. No code.</p><smart-layout variant=\"solidJoinedBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Input</h4><p>Text goes in</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>AI Step</h4><p>One node thinks</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Output</h4><p>Summary comes out</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/2FRTWLz2NsiFQ9Pk6Jkn7.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Honest Tool Talk</h1><p>Three tools dominate automation for recruiters. Here is how they compare honestly.</p><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Zapier</h4><p>Easiest to start. Gets expensive fast. Good for quick wins, not for scale.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Make</h4><p>Visual and powerful. Cheaper than Zapier. A strong middle ground for most teams.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>n8n</h4><p>Best value and power. The builders' standard. This course uses n8n. Everything transfers to Make.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"info\"><p>This course uses n8n. Every skill you build here transfers directly to Make.</p></aside></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/NRHhwoFexQFcIuufue604.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Your Accounts: All Free or Low Cost</h1><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" variant=\"processSteps\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/cloud.svg\"/><div><h4>n8n</h4><p>Cloud trial or self-hosted. Either works for this course.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/key.svg\"/><div><h4>An AI Key</h4><p>From Claude or OpenAI. This is a secret. Treat it like a password.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/file-spreadsheet.svg\"/><div><h4>Google Account with Sheets</h4><p>A free Google account is all you need. Sheets will store your results.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>n8n in Five Words</h1><display size=\"md\">Nodes. Lines. Trigger. Action. Flow.</display><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><span>Trigger</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><span>Action</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><span>Lines</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><span>Execute</span></div></div><p>A board of nodes connected by lines. A node is one step. A line passes data along. The first node is a trigger. The rest are actions. Press execute and watch the data flow.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Build the AI Summarizer: Four Boxes</h1><p>Open n8n and place these four nodes in order. Use dummy profile data only. Never use a real candidate. Use the name Alex R. for any example input.</p><smart-layout orientation=\"horizontal\" variant=\"arrows\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/play.svg\"/><div><h4>1. Manual Trigger</h4><p>Starts the workflow on demand</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/text.svg\"/><div><h4>2. Set Input Text</h4><p>Dummy profile for Alex R. Never a real candidate</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/brain.svg\"/><div><h4>3. AI Step</h4><p>Your Profile Summarizer prompt plus your AI key. This is the brain.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/eye.svg\"/><div><h4>4. See the Result</h4><p>The summary appears in the output panel</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"success\"><p>Press execute. The summary for Alex R. appears. You just ran your first AI automation.</p></aside></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>What You Just Proved</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>The Pattern</h4><p>No code. Four boxes. Three are plumbing, one does the thinking. That single thinking node is the AI step, and it is the only part that changes between builds.</p><p>This is the template for every build left in the course.</p></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Sourcing</h4><p>Find candidates</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Screening</h4><p>Score profiles</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Outreach</h4><p>Write messages</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/yzJzHorLSiZ1lpv8MePww.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Optional Stretch: Wire It to a Sheet</h1><p>Ready to go further? Swap two nodes and the workflow runs itself whenever a new row appears in your Google Sheet.</p><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/google.svg\"/><span>Sheets trigger</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/brain.svg\"/><span>AI summarize</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/i-cursor.svg\"/><span>Write summary</span></div></div><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>What Changes</h4><ul><li>Swap the manual trigger for a Google Sheets trigger set to fire on new row</li><li>Add a final Sheets node that writes the summary back to the same row</li></ul></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>What You Get</h4><p>A new row in your sheet produces a summary automatically. No button press needed. The workflow runs without you.</p><aside><p>Use a test sheet with dummy data only. Alex R. works perfectly here.</p></aside></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/24mHBuQy1pd6Rr3W082zq.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Next: Module 05</h1><h4>Build 1 - The Sourcing Agent</h4><p>It finds and lists candidates from free sources and writes a clean shortlist to a sheet. One workflow, real results.</p><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithTopCircle\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Have your n8n account ready</h4><p>Cloud trial or self-hosted, either works</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Have your AI key ready</h4><p>Claude or OpenAI, stored safely as a secret</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Have a Google Sheet ready</h4><p>A blank sheet to receive your shortlist</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"success\"><p>See you in Module 05. Ada will walk you through every node.</p></aside></div></div>"], "05": ["<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><h4>Module 05: Build 1, The Sourcing Agent</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/mumV_ZTRxY4x88NwKSHcK.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/8YHC44_DU7DQ34WgMm8cj.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>What You Will Build</h1><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Input</h4><p>An open role with requirements and location</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Process</h4><p>A Sourcing Agent that turns the role into a structured candidate shortlist</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Output</h4><p>The boring copying becomes automatic. The judgment stays with you.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>An Honest Definition</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><p>We do not scrape thousands of profiles. That breaks platform rules and risks candidate data.</p><aside variant=\"warning\"><p>Scraping violates platform terms and puts candidate data at risk.</p></aside></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Free Sources</h4><p>Only publicly available, free platforms are used.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Public Data</h4><p>Only visible, public information is collected.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Human in the Loop</h4><p>The searching stays with you. The structuring becomes automatic.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/YNJ4hiVXXRpQcHQo1M72W.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Shape: A Workflow with Two AI Steps</h1><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/user.svg\"/><span>Role In</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/keyboard.svg\"/><span>AI Builds Strings</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/clipboard.svg\"/><span>You Search and Paste</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/list.svg\"/><span>AI Structures List</span></div></div><p>Role in. AI builds search strings. You search free sources and paste public results. AI structures each into clean fields. A tidy shortlist comes out.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/HCOlZ8pwdbABpzTJEX4on.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 1 and 2: Capture the Role, Build the Searches</h1><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" variant=\"processSteps\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/heading.svg\"/><div><h4>Fill One Row</h4><p>Enter title, must-have skills, and location into a single row.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/sparkles.svg\"/><div><h4>AI Returns a Search Kit</h4><p>A boolean string, X-ray strings for LinkedIn, GitHub, and personal sites, plus alternative titles.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/bolt-lightning.svg\"/><div><h4>Seconds, Not Hours</h4><p>A complete search kit ready to use, generated in seconds.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 3: You Gather, From Free Sources</h1><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" source=\"image.ai-generated\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/mMFUGE8GiPpytffs_II4e.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><p>Run the strings across free, public platforms. Copy the visible info into a raw notes column, one row per person.</p><aside variant=\"info\"><p>You decide who is added. Every entry is a human choice.</p></aside></div></columns><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxesWithIconsInside\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/linkedin.svg\"/><div><h4>LinkedIn Search</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/google.svg\"/><div><h4>Google X-ray</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/github.svg\"/><div><h4>GitHub</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/business-time.svg\"/><div><h4>Portfolios</h4></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 4: The Second AI Step Structures the Results</h1><p>The AI reads each raw notes cell and extracts clean fields. Truth constraint: missing data is \"not stated,\" never invented.</p><table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Name</b></p></td><td><p><b>Title</b></p></td><td><p><b>Company</b></p></td><td><p><b>Skills</b></p></td><td><p><b>Why They Fit</b></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Alex R.</p></td><td><p>Senior Engineer</p></td><td><p>not stated</p></td><td><p>Python, AWS</p></td><td><p>Matches must-haves</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Sam T.</p></td><td><p>Full Stack Dev</p></td><td><p>Startup Co.</p></td><td><p>React, Node</p></td><td><p>Strong portfolio</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Jordan K.</p></td><td><p>Backend Lead</p></td><td><p>Tech Corp.</p></td><td><p>Go, Kubernetes</p></td><td><p>Relevant experience</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Twenty candidates structured in the time one used to take.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Clean Shortlist</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><p>One row per candidate. Identical columns for everyone. That consistency is what makes automated screening possible in the next module.</p><aside variant=\"success\"><p>Consistent structure unlocks automated scoring and ranking in Module 06.</p></aside></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Alex R.</h4><p>Senior Engineer - Python, AWS</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Sam T.</h4><p>Full Stack Dev - React, Node</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Jordan K.</h4><p>Backend Lead - Go, Kubernetes</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Rules Baked In</h1><smart-layout image-position=\"top\" variant=\"iconsText\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/openid.svg\"/><div><h4>Free Sources Only</h4><p>No paid scraping tools. No platform violations.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/eye.svg\"/><div><h4>Public Data Only</h4><p>Only information that is openly visible is collected.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/person.svg\"/><div><h4>Human Decides</h4><p>A human decides who is added to the shortlist. Always.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/comment.svg\"/><div><h4>Truth Constraint</h4><p>Missing data is \"not stated,\" never invented. Every AI step follows this rule.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><p>These four rules keep you and your candidates safe.</p></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/iLr_3bsoHReX8wjkfh1J2.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/bdM8QxKxUbSKwFaYb2xmt.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Next: Module 06</h1><display size=\"md\">Build 2: The Screening Agent</display><p>It scores every candidate against the must-haves and ranks them, before you read a single profile.</p><aside><p>Bring a populated shortlist from this module. You will need it.</p></aside><smart-layout variant=\"solidJoinedBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Module 05</h4><p>Sourcing Agent. Role in, shortlist out.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Module 06</h4><p>Screening Agent. Scores and ranks every candidate automatically.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>"], "06": ["<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/AhizLWRU5_XrFfCpl1tDJ.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><h4>Module 06: Build 2, The Screening Agent</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/kuCq0ffmPFnEoEcI6Ca-c.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Build That Saves the Most Hours</h1><p>Screening is where recruiters lose their evenings. The Screening Agent scores and ranks your whole shortlist, so the strongest candidates are already at the top.</p><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>You Still Decide</h4><p>The agent does not replace your judgment. It applies it.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Faster</h4><p>No more manually comparing every candidate one by one.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>More Consistently</h4><p>Every candidate is scored against the same criteria, every time.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Shape: One AI Step Across Every Row</h1><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/list.svg\"/><span>Shortlist In</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/robot.svg\"/><span>AI Scores</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/sort.svg\"/><span>Ranked Shortlist Out</span></div></div><p>For each candidate, the AI scores fit against your must-haves and writes a verdict, score, match, and risk. Then sort by score. A ranked shortlist comes out.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/uvoh5n-dHH9ObEePFC9qs.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 1: Define the Must-Haves Once</h1><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Write 3 to 6 Criteria</h4><p>Focus on the things that genuinely decide fit. Not a wish list. The real requirements.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Be Honest About Must vs. Nice to Have</h4><p>Mixing these two categories is the most common mistake. Keep them separate.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>This Is Your Judgment</h4><p>The agent applies your criteria. It does not invent them. The quality of the output depends on the quality of this step.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 2: The Scoring Step</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><p>Use your Fit Scorer prompt. For each candidate, the agent returns a fixed structure every single time.</p><table><tbody><tr><td><p><b>Field</b></p></td><td><p><b>What It Contains</b></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Verdict</p></td><td><p>Strong, Possible, or Weak</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Score</p></td><td><p>A number out of 10</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Must-Have Match</p></td><td><p>Which criteria are met</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>Top Risk</p></td><td><p>The single biggest concern</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><aside variant=\"info\"><p>Truth Constraint: Missing data is always recorded as \"not stated.\" The agent never invents information to fill a gap. This keeps scores honest and auditable.</p></aside><p>Example candidates scored: Alex R., Sam T., Jordan K.</p></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Reliability Tip: Same Format Every Time</h1><blockquote><p>Consistent output is what lets the workflow sort and rank. Inconsistent free text cannot be ranked.</p></blockquote><smart-layout variant=\"solidJoinedBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Structured Output</h4><p>Fixed fields. Fixed labels. The same shape for every candidate, every run.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Sortable Results</h4><p>Because the format is consistent, scores can be sorted and compared automatically.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Dependable Workflow</h4><p>This structured-output habit is exactly what made the Fit Analyzer dependable in earlier builds.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/TaJamCkyjVlNgRxEIrdEf.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 3: Rank and Flag</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img class=\"g-info\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/AmAVGgqrfWz8PLd2.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><p>Sort by score, highest first. Tag verdicts so the tiers are immediately visible.</p><smart-layout variant=\"arrowBullets\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Strong at the Top</h4><p>The candidates worth your immediate attention are right there.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Weak at the Bottom</h4><p>No time wasted. You can see at a glance who does not meet the bar.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Reasoning Visible</h4><p>Every score comes with the logic behind it. Nothing is a black box.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 4: You Review, Always</h1><p>The agent ranks. You decide. The score is a first pass, not a verdict on a person.</p><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithTopCircle\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Spot-Check the Reasons</h4><p>Do not just look at the scores. Read the reasoning behind them. A score without context is not enough.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Glance at Low Scores</h4><p>Check a few low-scoring candidates for unfair \"not stated\" penalties. Missing data is not the same as a bad fit.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>You Make the Call</h4><p>The agent surfaces the signal. The final decision belongs to you, the recruiter.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/VflGGyGXXR9TQ3BKV3gUT.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/VbPliUyWLQx4FcfncOGM1.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>A Word on Fairness</h1><blockquote><p>Score the skills, not the person.</p></blockquote><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div class=\"g-colorpanel\" style=\"background:#4A90D9;color:#fff;padding:14px 16px;border-radius:10px;flex:50 1 0\"><h4>Use Only Job-Relevant Criteria</h4><p>Every criterion in your scoring prompt must connect directly to the role. If it does not affect job performance, it does not belong.</p></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>What to Never Include</h4><ul><li>A candidate's name</li><li>Age or date of birth</li><li>Background or origin</li><li>Any protected characteristic</li></ul><aside variant=\"info\"><p>Full treatment of fairness and bias is covered in Module 09. But the habit starts now, in every prompt you write.</p></aside></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/aveBXmKbwTXTWHmCCtqho.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Next: Module 07</h1><h4>Build 3: The Outreach Agent</h4><p>For your top-ranked candidates, the Outreach Agent drafts a personalized first message in your voice, ready to review and send. Bring your ranked shortlist.</p><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Input</h4><p>Your ranked shortlist from the Screening Agent. Alex R., Sam T., and any other strong candidates.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Output</h4><p>A personalized first message for each top candidate, written in your voice.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Your Role</h4><p>Review and send. The agent drafts. You approve. Fast, personal, and consistent.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>"], "07": ["<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/y3rgjB14eoQthaxmQF1eb.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><h4>Module 07: Build 3, The Outreach Agent</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/7X-lG7662ONVahDmjCqJX.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Last Mile</h1><p>You sourced and screened. Now the Outreach Agent drafts a personalized first message for every top candidate, in your voice, using what you actually know about them.</p><smart-layout variant=\"solidJoinedBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Source</h4><p>Find and structure top candidates</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Screen</h4><p>Rank and evaluate the shortlist</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Outreach</h4><p>Draft a personal first message. You review and send.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Rule That Does Not Move</h1><blockquote><p>It drafts. You review and send.</p></blockquote><p>This build never sends on its own. A human is always the last step before a candidate is contacted.</p><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><aside variant=\"warning\"><p>Never auto-sends. The workflow creates a draft only. The send button stays with you.</p></aside></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><aside variant=\"success\"><p>Scales your personal touch. Not replaces it. Every message still carries your judgment and voice.</p></aside></div></columns></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/p9X7yTQE3CE-nIgdfHjL3.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Shape of the Workflow</h1><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/list.svg\"/><span>Ranked Shortlist</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/robot.svg\"/><span>AI Drafts Message</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/inbox.svg\"/><span>Draft to Review</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/send-backward.svg\"/><span>Review and Send</span></div></div><p>The pipeline is simple by design. A ranked shortlist enters. For each candidate, the AI drafts a message in your voice. Each draft lands in a column. You review, edit, and send. Nothing moves forward without your approval.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 1: Capture Your Voice</h1><p>A message in a voice that is not yours is still a template. Paste two or three real messages you are proud of into the Outreach Drafter as your tone reference. The model copies your rhythm.</p><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Why real messages matter</h4><p>The model learns your sentence length, your word choices, and your level of formality. Generic prompts produce generic output. Your examples produce your voice.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Two or three is enough</h4><p>You do not need a large sample. Two strong examples give the model enough signal to match your rhythm and tone consistently across every draft.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/GKalDmoJBq_kvk_GcD_mx.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 2: Feed It Real, Specific Context</h1><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" source=\"image.ai-generated\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/lc-DR-gGlIfx6Xhk2-Fpz.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><p>Generic outreach could have been sent to anyone. Personal outreach could only have been sent to that person.</p><ul><li>Use their current role and specific skill</li><li>Include the why-they-fit line</li><li>Only facts from their candidate row</li><li>No invented details, ever</li></ul><aside variant=\"caution\"><p>Truth constraint: The agent uses only facts present in the candidate row. It does not invent details, fill gaps, or assume context.</p></aside></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 3: The Drafting Step</h1><p>For each candidate on the shortlist, the agent produces a structured short message. Drafts fill a review column, ready for your eyes.</p><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxesWithIconsInside\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/webhook.svg\"/><div><h4>One specific opening hook</h4><p>Tied to something real about Alex R., Sam T., or Jordan K. Not a generic opener.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/briefcase.svg\"/><div><h4>One sentence on the role</h4><p>Clear and direct. What the role is and why it is worth a conversation.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/question.svg\"/><div><h4>A low-pressure question</h4><p>Invites a reply without demanding commitment. Easy to say yes to.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/scissors.svg\"/><div><h4>Under 90 words, no filler</h4><p>No \"Hope this finds you well.\" No padding. Every word earns its place.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 4: You Review, Edit, and Send</h1><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/passport.svg\"/><span>Read Draft</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/i-cursor.svg\"/><span>Fix Voice</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/mailbox.svg\"/><span>Send from Gmail</span></div></div></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><h4>Your review checklist</h4><ul><li>Read each draft against the candidate profile</li><li>Fix the voice if it drifts from yours</li><li>Cut, do not add. Shorter is better.</li><li>Send from Gmail. The workflow creates a draft only.</li></ul><aside variant=\"info\"><p>The workflow can create a Gmail draft. It cannot auto-send. The human send stays human, always.</p></aside></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/DSbjXPPwBAMcyw_j9VjHy.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>What This Completes</h1><p>Three builds. One pipeline. Each reads the output of the one before it.</p><smart-layout orientation=\"vertical\" variant=\"arrows\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/searchengin.svg\"/><div><h4>Sourcing</h4><p>Finds and structures candidates into a ranked list</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/filter.svg\"/><div><h4>Screening</h4><p>Ranks and evaluates the shortlist by fit</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/envelope.svg\"/><div><h4>Outreach</h4><p>Drafts a personal first message for every top candidate</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/ijx9q62_33-qEp57AJ8Rj.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Next: Module 08</h1><h4>Your Recruiting Operating System</h4><p>Connect all three builds end to end, with one place to run a role through the whole pipeline. Bring all three builds.</p><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>What to bring</h4><p>Your Sourcing Agent, your Screening Agent, and your Outreach Agent. All three connect in Module 08.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>What you will build</h4><p>One unified operating system. One place to run a role from first search to first message sent.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>"], "08": ["<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><h4>Module 08: Your Recruiting Operating System</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/kCNbX2-ttlwijZOecOcQA.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>From Three Tools to One System</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><p>You have three working builds. Today they become one connected system.</p><p>That shift is the difference between someone who uses AI and someone who runs an operation on it.</p></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Before</h4><p>Three separate tools running independently</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>After</h4><p>One connected system with a single outcome</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/uycKvORQpgMspCCHBNreY.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/W8DUHY3gxEGQ2TkKovuf1.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Operating System Framing</h1><blockquote><p>You are not running a screening workflow. You are running the system that runs your recruiting desk.</p></blockquote><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>The Input</h4><p>A role requirement enters the system.</p></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><h4>The Output</h4><p>A reviewed, ready-to-send shortlist comes out. That is the outcome worth paying for.</p></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>The Whole Pipeline, One Sheet</h1><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/magnifying-glass.svg\"/><span>Sourcing</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/star-half-stroke.svg\"/><span>Screening</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/paperclip.svg\"/><span>Outreach</span></div></div><p>By the end, every candidate is one row with everything attached. Sourcing, scoring, and outreach drafts live in a single place, giving you a complete picture at a glance.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 1: One Master Sheet with a Status Column</h1><smart-layout numbered=\"false\" variant=\"pills\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/searchengin.svg\"/><div><h4>Sourced</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/bars.svg\"/><div><h4>Screened</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/pencil.svg\"/><div><h4>Drafted</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/send-backward.svg\"/><div><h4>Sent</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/reply.svg\"/><div><h4>Replied</h4></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/x.svg\"/><div><h4>Rejected</h4></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><p>The status column is the spine. Each agent acts on rows at a status and moves them to the next. You always know where every candidate stands.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 2: Chain the Agents</h1><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><span>Sourced</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><span>Screened</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><span>Moved</span></div></div></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><h4>Status-Driven Logic</h4><p>Each workflow acts only on rows at its input status.</p><smart-layout variant=\"arrowBullets\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Screening</h4><p>Processes rows with status: Sourced</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Outreach</h4><p>Processes rows with status: Screened, above threshold only</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"success\"><p>Simple, transparent, and easy to debug.</p></aside></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 3: Where the Human Stays</h1><p>The agents handle the volume. You handle the judgment.</p><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" orientation=\"vertical\" variant=\"outlineBoxesWithLabel\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Add a Candidate</h4><p>You decide who enters the system.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Set the Must-Haves</h4><p>You define the criteria that matter.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Review the Ranking</h4><p>You validate the agent's scoring output.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Review and Send Outreach</h4><p>You approve every message before it goes out.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>The Hire Decision</h4><p>You make the final call. Always.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Step 4: Keep It Reliable and Simple</h1><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" source=\"image.ai-generated\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/nQTBnqtog3VIVtANcby9L.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Fail Loud, Not Silent</h4><p>Flag error rows. Do not skip them. A silent failure is worse than a visible one.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Spot-Check Weekly</h4><p>Review a sample of agent outputs every week to catch drift early.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Resist Adding More</h4><p>The smallest system that runs your desk well is the goal. Complexity is the enemy.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Sell the Operating System, Not the Wiring</h1><blockquote><p>Nobody buys three chained workflows. They buy the outcome: a role in, a reviewed shortlist out, in a fraction of the time, every time.</p></blockquote><smart-layout variant=\"solidJoinedBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>What You Built</h4><p>Three agents chained by a status column in a master sheet</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>What You Sell</h4><p>Hours returned. Shortlists delivered. Consistent results at scale.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><p>Lead with the hours returned. The wiring is your competitive advantage, not your pitch.</p></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/-wWkEVbW2vZDvEqyccHKI.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Next: Module 09</h1><h4>Responsible AI and Making It Pay</h4><smart-layout image-position=\"left\" variant=\"iconsText\"><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/shield.svg\"/><div><h4>Candidate Data and Consent</h4><p>How to handle personal data responsibly inside your system.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/scale-balanced.svg\"/><div><h4>Fairness</h4><p>Identifying and reducing bias in agent scoring and outreach.</p></div></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><img class=\"g-icon\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/_app_static/icons/v0/clock.svg\"/><div><h4>Measuring Hours and Money Saved</h4><p>Quantifying the return on your operating system investment.</p></div></smart-layout-item></smart-layout><aside variant=\"info\"><p>Bring your running system and your Module 00 Time Audit to the next session.</p></aside></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/8g2hdSTCcyACcXH_-s17x.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>"], "09": ["<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/i5Zz8vMF20CvlgHNHa3J3.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>AI Agents for Tech Recruiters and Headhunters</h1><h4>Module 09: Responsible AI and Making It Pay</h4><p>Narrated by Ada, your AI course host</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/c54PijTGD7gZdgRmRP3EA.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Two Final Jobs</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Run It Safely</h4><p>Candidate data, fairness, transparency. A system you cannot trust will not last.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Prove It Works</h4><p>Measure the time and money saved. A system you cannot justify will not last.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Handle Candidate Data Responsibly</h1><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxesWithSideLine\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Collect Less, On Purpose</h4><p>Public sources only. Minimize what you hold from the start.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Know the GDPR Basics</h4><p>Lawful reason, transparency, minimization, retention, deletion.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Control Access</h4><p>Limit who can see candidate data inside your system.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Never Let AI Invent Facts</h4><p>Every data point about a person must be verifiable and real.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/_bvfNSnUwYRWtrYQLaLvB.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Keep Screening Fair</h1><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><img alt=\"\" source=\"image.ai-generated\" src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/FG9fgpkTYPUPs-VMM4ChM.png\"/></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><smart-layout numbered=\"false\" variant=\"bigBullets\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Score on Job-Relevant Criteria Only</h4><p>Skills and experience. Nothing else.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Never Name Protected Attributes</h4><p>No age, gender, school, background, or name in scoring logic.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Keep a Human on Every Decision</h4><p>Watch for proxies. Audit occasionally. Fair screening is better screening.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/NZlL4sDsGF5cyiKghOlu9.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Be Transparent with Candidates</h1><blockquote><p>\"It helps me organize and prioritize. I make the decisions.\"</p></blockquote><smart-layout variant=\"solidJoinedBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>AI Helped Structure and Rank</h4><p>The system organized and scored the pipeline.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>A Human Reviewed Everyone</h4><p>Every person contacted was reviewed by you first.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>You Sent Every Message</h4><p>Honest and reassuring. Candidates deserve to know.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Make It Pay: Measure the After</h1><columns col-widths=\"[65,35]\"><div style=\"flex:65 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><div class=\"g-diagram\"><div class=\"g-step\"><span>Before: Manual Audit</span></div><div class=\"g-step\"><span>After: AI-Assisted</span></div></div></div><div style=\"flex:35 1 0\" vertical-align=\"center\"><h4>Your Before Picture</h4><p>Pull out your Module 00 Time Audit. That is your baseline.</p><h4>Run a Real Role</h4><p>Take one live role through the full system. Track the same time buckets you measured before.</p><h4>Find the Gap</h4><p>The difference between before and after is your time saved per role.</p></div></columns></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Translate Time into Money</h1><smart-layout variant=\"stats\"><smart-layout-item label=\"x hrs\"><h4>Hours Saved Per Month</h4><p>Multiply by your hourly value to get your direct saving.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item label=\"+roles\"><h4>Extra Roles You Can Run</h4><p>Each additional placement multiplies your upside.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item label=\"faster\"><h4>Faster Shortlists</h4><p>Faster shortlists can mean faster placements and faster fees.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/Fi_7MH95IhFOn9uDXkTPb.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-left\"><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/vet595_QRUfnIgr6qEoeF.png\" alt=\"\"></div><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Write the One-Line Business Case</h1><blockquote><p>\"This system gives me back about N hours a week, roughly X per month, and lets me run M more roles at once.\"</p></blockquote><p>That one sentence justifies the system. It is your pitch to yourself, your clients, and your business.</p><aside variant=\"success\"><p>One sentence. Specific numbers. Written down. Done.</p></aside></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-full\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>Sell the Outcome, Not the Tooling</h1><columns col-widths=\"[50,50]\"><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><smart-layout variant=\"outlineBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Not This</h4><p>\"I will build you workflows and automations.\"</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div style=\"flex:50 1 0\"><smart-layout variant=\"solidBoxes\"><smart-layout-item><h4>Say This Instead</h4><p>\"I will give your desk back N hours a week and a more consistent shortlist.\"</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div></columns><p>Price against the value, not your build hours. Clients buy outcomes. Lead with the outcome every time.</p></div></div>", "<div class=\"slide slide-right\"><div class=\"slide-body\"><h1>You Run the System Now</h1><smart-layout numbered=\"true\" variant=\"processSteps\"><smart-layout-item><h4>You Started a Beginner</h4><p>No agents, no prompt library, no system.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>You Built the Foundation</h4><p>A prompt library, three agents, and one Operating System.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>You Made It Safe and Justified It</h4><p>Responsible data handling and a clear business case.</p></smart-layout-item><smart-layout-item><h4>Now Go Run a Real Role</h4><p>Your time is for judgment and relationships. Then teach one person.</p></smart-layout-item></smart-layout></div><div class=\"slide-art\"><img src=\"https://cdn.gamma.app/3ty6dzzbhnwrkmv/generated-images/IXPIwkQ2JjCRAPa808mN6.png\" alt=\"\"></div></div>"]};
